V’z Fine Dining event venue
.entry-header
Fine dining atmosphere, ready for your event….
Welcome to V’z
Our Delicious Story
V’z is named for Vincent Posada, an award winning chef who has brought the best of his career to Bartow Florida. With glowing chandeliers, stained glass and beautiful artwork, it is the perfect setting for your gathering. Whether it’s a family gathering or corporate event, we can customize set up and menus to suit your needs.
Available for Lunch or Dinner Functions, receptions to sit down meals. Call Cary to make your function a reality. 863-800-3181
.entry-content .clear
